main event: A few boys saw quite a few UFOs in Bedford, Ohio on May 9, 1965.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 6 to 8 minutes.
The witnesses were unable to provide any further details about the UFOs.
The witnesses wished to remain anonymous.
The Air Force concluded its investigation of UFOs, known as Project Blue Book, and found no evidence of a threat to national security or of any scientific importance.
The responsibility for investigating UFOs now rests with NASA, and the Air Force will continue to forward any reports to NASA.
